,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔識balance sheet都搵黎講 小學生都做到皇帝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99738eaea7c16d79f125339aed1e0d1e237abf18","tid":2431090,"uid":300630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"所以佢重熊大賺幾個億"},{"pid":"460ce97383d089e211919295447898d7c722e219","tid":2431090,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"食屎狗<br />\n要不是美國人, 你死撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af8efff631e5ec8e5600f84a39d448f18fa082c","tid":2431090,"uid":69841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"「我不想兒女這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n所以啲兒女去哂英國先<br />\n全港市民啲兒女要為五斗米折腰就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5390268c9f3c8fce3afcf495ef41722fd4a27d1","tid":2431090,"uid":303686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啦， 乜都夠膽做！"},{"pid":"bf0ffa7e665589548835346e2925485e134b317c","tid":2431090,"uid":6297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"「所以在我人生，我眼裏只要錢，只要有錢我可以出賣靈魂，賣女去做雞都得」"},{"pid":"4c4e91b895ab109853eb5d8f3e9dca0e353b5920","tid":2431090,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"收爹啦"},{"pid":"c89625d41db07d06a3cc26e061d8d3e572e815a0","tid":2431090,"uid":32837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母陳茂波<br />\n你而家搞到香港市民愈嚟愈窮呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"af3aba0292c8832d2ff09c14136b584d7160d3ac","tid":2431090,"uid":299433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"運過毒都可以做高官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7d32e0482cf9a5d34d487e0f3233f563af7dde","tid":2431090,"uid":40397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"